&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;brew install cmake
brew install glib
brew install pkg-config
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;build-and-run&#34;&gt;Build and Run&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;mkdir -p build &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; build
cmake .. &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; make

&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# run&lt;/span&gt;
./glib-playground
